# Replace with a valid token from POST /api/sessions
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create discount — percent (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/discounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "10% Off", "type": "percent", "amount": 10 }

###

### Create discount — fixed (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/discounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "$2 Off", "type": "fixed", "amount": 2.00 }

###

### Create discount — invalid type (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/discounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "Bad", "type": "bogus", "amount": 5 }

###

### Create discount — percent over 100 (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/discounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "Too Much", "type": "percent", "amount": 150 }

###

### Get all active discounts (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/discounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get discount by id (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update discount (expect 200)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/discounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "15% Off", "type": "percent", "amount": 15 }

###

### Delete (soft) discount (expect 204)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get deleted discount by id (expect 200, isActive: false)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
